  "slug": "a-house-of-dynamite-is-ready-to-explode",
  "title": "‘A House of Dynamite’ Is Ready to Explode",
  "show": "The Big Picture",
  "network": "The Ringer",
  "hosts": [
    "Sean Fennessey",
    "Amanda Dobbins"
  ],
  "published": "2025-10-27",
  "runtimeMin": 105,
  "format": "Sean and Amanda review Kathryn Bigelow's real-time nuclear-attack thriller 'A House of Dynamite,' now on Netflix: a first hour that had them locked in, and a third act (Idris Elba's miscast president, an on-the-nose ending) that lost them. Plus a bleak-October box-office check-in, and Adam Naiman joins to talk Kelly Reichardt's 'The Mastermind.'",
  "segments": [
    {
