      "heading": "The state of the box office",
      "note": "anime up top, adult dramas going quietly",
      "films": [
        {
          "title": "Chainsaw Man – The Movie: Reze Arc",
          "year": 2025,
          "note": "No. 1 in America, Sony distributing anime the way it did 'Demon Slayer' a month earlier. Sean hasn't seen it; the hosts read the run as proof that fandom, not walk-up discovery, now drives the box office."
        },
        {
          "title": "Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle",
          "year": 2025,
          "note": "The other Sony anime hit cited as evidence something is changing about who turns out for theaters."
